com.sap.cloud.sdk.cloudplatform.auditlog

Class ScpCfAuditLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.cloudplatform.auditlog.ScpCfAuditLog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuditLog

    public class ScpCfAuditLog
extends Object
implements AuditLog
    Implementation of audit logging that uses the Cloud Foundry (HANA XS) library. The cloudplatform library is very limited, so audit data is filled in on a best effort basis.

    Important: For performance reasons, use only for logging of events as required by the relevant security standards:

    • SEC-215 "SAP software shall be able to log security relevant events."
    • SEC-254 "SAP software shall log read access to sensitive personal data."
    • SEC-257 "SAP software shall be able to log changes to configuration data."
    • SEC-265 "SAP software shall log changes to personal data."
        Future enhancements:
        • Use class name of caller provided by factory
        • Fill in tenant information
